Package: CspStandSegmentation
Type: Package
Title: Comparative Shortest Path Stand Segmentation
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Dr. Julian Frey
Maintainer: Dr. Julian Frey <julian.frey@iww.uni-freiburg.de>
Description: This package provides a function to segment trees from a stand scanned with terrestrial laser scanning. It strongly builds uppon the work of the lidR and the TreeLS packages.
